            "description": "## GetAllUsers\n\nRetrieves a paginated list of all users from the API.\n\n### Query Parameters\n\n| Parameter | Type | Description |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| `pageSize` | integer | The number of users to return per page. Default: `5`. |\n| `pageNumber` | integer | The zero-based index of the page to retrieve. Default: `0`. |\n\n### Notes\n\n- **`pageNumber`** **is zero-based** — the first page is `0`, the second is `1`, and so on.\n    \n- Adjust `pageSize` to control the volume of results returned in a single request.\n    \n- Use `pageNumber` in combination with `pageSize` to paginate through the full list of users."
          },
          "response": []
        },
