            "description": "## Add User\n\nCreates a new user in the system.\n\n**Method:** `POST`  \n**URL:** `{{endpoint}}user`\n\n### Request Body\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"user1\"\n}\n```\n\n| Field | Type   | Description                        |\n|-------|--------|------------------------------------|\n| `name` | string | The name of the user to be created |\n\n### Expected Behavior\n\nUpon a successful request, a new user is created with the provided `name`."
