            "description": "## UpdateUser\n\nUpdates an existing user's information by their user ID.\n\n**Method:** PUT  \n**URL:** `{{endpoint}}user/{id}`\n\n## Path Parameters\n\n| Parameter | Description |\n| --- | --- |\n| `id` | The unique identifier of the user to update (e.g. `10`) |\n\n## Request Body\n\nSend a JSON object with the fields you want to update.\n\n``` json\n{\n    \"name\": \"superuser\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n| Field | Type | Description |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| `name` | string | The new name for the user |\n\n## Response\n\nReturns the updated user object on success."
